{"type": "article", "id": 26086, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-04-28T07:04:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 26843, "name": "Lady Hio"}, {"id": 26844, "name": "D-TWELVE"}, {"id": 26845, "name": "Plato Design"}, {"id": 26846, "name": "BeoPlay A1"}, {"id": 26847, "name": "Fumo Wallet"}, {"id": 26871, "name": "S1"}, {"id": 250, "name": "Philippe Starck"}, {"id": 13757, "name": "Bang & Olufsen"}, {"id": 26848, "name": "PuffTec"}, {"id": 26849, "name": "Good Chemistry"}, {"id": 26850, "name": "Confederation Studio"}, {"id": 26872, "name": "Klafs"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607121521W8FDz43kYbfqHsy2.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>Lady Hio by Philippe Starck</h2>\n<p class=\"medium-insert-images-wide\">这一系列的玻璃桌名为 Lady Hio，由 <a href=\"http://www.starck.com/en/\">Philippe Starck</a> 和 <a href=\"http://www.schito.com/\">S. Schito’s</a> 联合打造。管状的桌腿是它的一大亮点，用硼硅玻璃进行吹制，两端的阳极氧化铝合金则起到了连接桌面和固定的作用。整体造型非常优雅，并有黄、暖灰、橙三种颜色可供选择。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135829V1hltIS8qE2739Wz.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135830hA8QHWNTipy2wYCM.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135830u6EJHr5K1mzyQLWd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135831YQ7XWc5yfM4u3VBZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135831KUmynWRiGO6b4Jht.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>D-TWELVE by Plato Design</h2>\n<p class=\"\">这款磁性多功能组合灯由双人设计师组合 Plato Design 出品，名叫 D-TWELVE。通过表面附着的磁贴，你可以将它们自由地组合在一起形成凸显个性的照明系统。当然，哪怕只是将独立的一盏摆放在桌上，也非常吸引眼球。你可以通过 <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1843649997/d-twelve-lamp-the-modular-magnetic-lighting-system\">Kickstarter </a>了解更多相关信息。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071358328nzjqehAx2gNBJLE.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66715758\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135832m3M7Efz6WbSO09Ht.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61323529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071358330C7bi9DpmQqU31P6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33529412\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135833li2HgfRxzJF90cDS.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.43529412\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135834RZMqLYBabSDs5Gvh.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>BeoPlay A1 by Bang &amp; Olufsen</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.beoplay.com/\">BeoPlay A1</a> 是丹麦品牌 Bang &amp; Olufsen 最新推出的一款蓝牙扬声器，小巧精致的造型强调出的是便携性，对于大大小小的派对场合来说非常实用。铝合金外壳表面的触感光滑，没有设计凸起的操纵按钮，总重量约为 590 克。你还可以下载一个 <a href=\"http://www.beoplay.com/products/beoplayapp#pairing\" onclick=\"recordOutboundLink(this, 'Linkout', 'http://www.beoplay.com/products/beoplayapp#pairing'); return true;\" target=\"_blank\">BeoPlay app</a> 来控制它播放音乐，很有科技感。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135836kDJl4toMifxZcuVe.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135837nxuEyTelKD3sVrOt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135837kDWTBCuJ4slK0XzU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135838fcO3NhEp4q1oDAVT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69259259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Fumo Wallet by PuffTec</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://pufftec.com/products/pufftec-wallet\">Fumo Wallet</a> 是夏威夷品牌 PuffTec 针对卷烟爱好者推出的一款手制皮革钱包。即便你无意放入卷烟装备，各类丰富的夹层和口袋不仅美观，也能满足你其他的收纳需求（比方说，它是以一台 iPhone 6 尺寸所设计的，完全可以用作手机套）。钱包采用的是意大利进口的皮革，每只售价为 300 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135838xubP2l5zMhOKdFnt.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071358393DZNlysL147ncvje.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135839JXEywlevh2orkU57.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135840Uqouny3MbRm8cszj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135840DTg0uSvrF5ZPmU2G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135841a7zZGtIqnkOv5Tw2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Good Chemistry by Confederation Studio</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://goodchemistrybrewing.com/\">Good Chemistry</a> 是一家酿酒初创公司，委托 <a href=\"http://confederationstudio.com/\">Confederation Studio</a> 负责品牌设计。外包装上采用的信息图很直观地阐述了每款啤酒的特性，与简洁明了的排版结合，带给人一种 geek 的感觉。这也正是创始人——啤酒爱好者 Bob 和 Kelly 这对情侣的意图，那就是让更多人了解啤酒世界的趣闻。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071358423l4gLY0nEkcZQ261.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135842aNMonz1i5cGpPS0u.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071358433dPEZY5UlNXb82SV.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135843A74NsjFlUKc8S50I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135844a8D4TIPXRjpd2m3k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071358442ipz6W4LO3eYINqo.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>S1 by Klafs</h2>\n<p class=\"\">如果你有一个在家蒸桑拿的梦想，德国公司 <a href=\"http://www.klafs.com/\">Klafs</a> 最新推出的这款延展式桑拿房 S1 可以帮你美梦成真。S1 的大小和一个书柜相当，可延展的空间共有三层——按下控制面板上的按钮，只需 20 秒，60 厘米深的空间就能完全展开。S1 内部所使用的木材比普通桑拿房内使用的要轻上 40%，Klafs 还为它配备了一个镶嵌式的照明灯和几个可以通过蓝牙和手机连接的扬声器。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135845Y3AxCNHKhdc2VZko.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.41666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135845d64C5fXeSWyTnuQG.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65281174\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135846MEki01lu725rKHTF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61246944\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135846rbkBaUMJVN3iGlm8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135847aDEkNIF3X8sqM9bu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607135847GDKBflT19R6gUXIw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}